item.title: How long ago did you register?
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

[quote=“Ruby, post:73, topic:518039”]I remember someone saying somewhere that jme edited his to look that way, or it was some happy accident or something. You can see the real registration dates by looking at the profile numbers: iirc jme is 4, Moparisthebest is 1.

CONSPIRACY.[/quote]

Yes at one point I changed my registration date. When it got changed back to normal the time was 12am (arhams must be different from timezone). I would have joined sometime between 01:42:13 PM and 01:43:58 PM going by user id’s, on feb 22 2006

As explained in the other thread

The forums were running a good month or two before Feb 22 2006 with over 100 members, so I wasn’t technically the 4th anyways. Everything was reset to new on the 22nd and I was on IRC when this happened. By the looks of it, Niall and Silab were probably on the IRC at that time too.
